Well, guys, I really didn't expect to generate this amount of dialog. I just wanted to put some words down expressing my dismay and concern at the hate and lies and bitterness here.  I can easily see that it comes from both sides and Barry Spatz is not in this alone. I do feel that you have been suckered in by imposters and trolls who have deliberately pushed your buttons. As adults who have a passion for what we believe in and concern for those of us who agree with those passions;  Step back a minute.  Look objectively at some of these posts. Take the innuendo out  and look! Guys, I really think you have been sucker punched. I think Spatz and others here really have better things to do with their lives than continue this rant. I feel every time that reconsiliation has gotten near, &quot;Spatz&quot; pushes Barela's button or Art's button.  I think a troll has been working you guys. The inflammatory remarks are insidious! These remarks stike at the very core of our beliefs!  They attack everything that we hold dear and sacred in our lives! I really do think the site has been sucked in.<br>
Been fine guys, just real busy!  Thanks for asking.  But watch your six!! Step back and look at this thing like I did.
